---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Your privacy matters. Here's how we handle your data."
>
  <section>
    <h2>GDPR and Commercial Status</h2>
    <p>This site uses cookies and may store some personal information. This site is managed by a natural person and has no commercial character, thus it is not under the effects of GDPR.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>We don't sell your data</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. Your data is used strictly to provide Meterly's service to you and your tenants or landlords.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>We don't run ads</h2>
    <p>Meterly is free of advertisements. We don't track your behavior or share your usage patterns with advertisers.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Stored information</h2>
    <p>We store the following information:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 m-0" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
      <li>Your account information (name, email address).</li>
      <li>Properties you create and their associated data.</li>
      <li>Meter readings, custom charges, and bills you submit.</li>
      <li>Photographs of utility bills (if uploaded).</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is used only to calculate and display bills to you and the tenants you invite.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files saved on your computer, containing various information required by the page. The most prominent example is keeping you logged in without the need to authenticate every once in a while. This website uses the following cookies:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 m-0" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
      <li><strong>Authentication Cookies:</strong> We use Better Auth to manage user sessions securely, which requires cookies to keep you logged in.</li>
      <li><strong>Security Cookies:</strong> We use Cloudflare cookies for DDoS protection and to ensure the security of our platform. For more details, see <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/fundamentals/reference/policies-compliances/cloudflare-cookies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-text); text-decoration: underline;">Cloudflare's cookie policy</a>.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data security</h2>
    <p>Your account and billing information are secured using industry-standard encryption. Access to property data is strictly isolated to the property owner and their assigned tenants.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact us</h2>
    <p>Questions about your privacy or our data practices? Email us at <a href="mailto:meterly.support@protonmail.com" class="email-link">meterly.support@protonmail.com</a></p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
